						               													<description>It is made up of three games efficiently articulated in an ECOAVENTURA, giving rise to a new and effective project of Environmental Education Entertaining for the whole family, where the excitement of throwing the dice; the decision whether or not to change a letter; the right strategy to recycle each waste in a timely manner; expectation about each question; solidarity in being able to rescue players who have not reached the goal; the concern about sanctions and the surprises of the benefits, will allow each player, not only to add the ECOpoints necessary to be the winner, but will build, almost without perceiving it, a solid and unforgettable environmental knowledge, that will allow to accelerate that change of attitude that is required to minimize, or better yet, to reduce, the events of Global Warming, which is affecting our planet so much.&amp;#10;DESCRIPTION OF THE GAMES&amp;#10;&amp;bull;    Our biggest challenge was to create games where you could combine knowledge, strategy, decisions, solidarity, expectation, and that your players not only have fun, but in doing so acquire the necessary knowledge to take care of their future.&amp;#10;&amp;bull;    The complete Kit consists of three (3) games, and in each of them   we have considered different concepts about the environmental problem, which is affecting our planet, adapting them in an entertaining way to the family language. The three games are:&amp;#10;1.  ECOTRIVIA:   Containing 648 Questions related to the environmental issue and the ECOCARDS game.&amp;#10;2.  ECOCARDS: 2 Decks of Cards, using the 4 elements of nature: Earth, Air, Water and Fire, containing 54 EcoTips and 54 EcoVips.&amp;#10;3.  RECYCARDS: where only with the right strategy you will be able to recycle all waste.&amp;#10;&amp;bull;    The great appeal is that the 3 games although they can be enjoyed independently, we have articulated them in a single Main Game, creating an entertaining ECO Adventure.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Play, get fun and learn in this ECOadventure to become into a Guardian of your Future! YOUR MISSION &amp;quot;SAVE THE PLANET&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
